{"tid":1560901,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港年輕人 大家性情近","createTime":"2019-09-11T11:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T12:00:34.000Z","uid":199861,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33220a38ef5421137894baa3797625ed1c2a78b0","tid":1560901,"uid":199861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lUu5VnuXTvg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlUu5VnuXTvg&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=5429f402\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lUu5VnuXTvg</a><br />\n<br />\n琴晚發覺好多老一輩既人都冇返開教會<br />\n落到場支持但係唔識唱<br />\n所以改左首歌希望巴打們一齊集思廣益<br />\n一家大細一齊唱<br />\n<br />\n光復香港年輕人 大家性情近<br />\n早出晚歸要隱密 永不篤灰互信任<br />\n時代革命雖艱辛 幸好有良朋<br />\n只要決心渡苦難 最終做個自由民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPS0sWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPS0sWE.jpg&h=bfe42da1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c51973d61b8b28c26b42937f104ce5c67d8f8f7d","tid":1560901,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"86e2645e2c3f4ef80ec79619f3d821106ebf4d20","tid":1560901,"uid":199861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"